[[File:Chlorine ampoule.jpg|thumb|[[Koloriin]] waa [[neef]] midabkeedu yahay huruud iyo cagaar isku dhafan, inta badana waxay u sameeysantahay [[labo]] [[atom]] oo isku xidhan.]]

