Waxay la fal-gashaa dhamaan [[bir]]ta iyo xoogaa [[Bir Ma Ahe]] ah, sida [[Kaarboon]]ka. 

Salfarta waxa la helaa ayadoo dabiici ah iyo ayadoo isku-dhis loo yaqaabo ''salfayt'' ah. 

[[Salfar]]ta waxaa isticmaali jirey [[wakhti]]yo hore wadanada [[Hindiya]], [[Shiinaha]], [[Masar]] iyo giriiga. 

[[Isku dhis]]yada [[curiye]]han wuxuu leeyahay faa'iido badan, oo inta u badan waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu ''bacarimiyo'' [[caro]]da iyo [[beer]]aha. Sidoo kale waxaa loo isticmaalaa in laga sameeyo [[taraqa]], [[sun]]ta [[Xasharaad]]ka iyo [[sun]]ta fangaha. 

Curiyahan meel dhexe ayuu kaga jiraa [[Diwaanka Curiye]]ha. 


